   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00154"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00153"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb655" type="place"><hi rend="capitals">Hotel Kaiserkrone</hi></rs></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">Bad Ischl</rs>, am <c rendition="#dots" n="10"/></hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place"><hi rend="capitals">Bad Ischl</hi></rs></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Zentrale Lage</hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Restaurationsgarten, Bäder</hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Lift, moderner Komfort</hi></hi></seg><salute>Viele Grüsse, lieber Arthur,</salute></opener><p>Ihnen und <rs ref="#pmb2173" type="person">Olga</rs>. Ich ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>e alle 3–4 Tage für 24 Stunden herüber. Vielleicht
               besuchen Sie <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11737" subtype="implied">Papa</rs> einmal, es
               ist ganz nahe, <rs ref="#pmb33909" type="place">Tänzlgasse 10</rs>,
                  <time>vormittag</time> sitzt er i<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>er in seinem
               Garten.</p><closer>Von Herzen Ihr<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
